com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi

Interface ITsapiCSTAUniversalFailure


  • public interface ITsapiCSTAUniversalFailure
    The list of universal failure codes that can be returned in CSTA UniversalFailure unsolicited events and confirmation events. This is useful, for example, for JTAPI exceptions thrown by the Avaya implementation which return these values.
